=== Description ===
Survive as long as possible.
You can't take many hits from the negative (red) energy!
Hold the left mouse button in your energy sphere to charge up, then
draw a path to an approaching enemies.

=== Compile ===
Dependencies you'll need for compiling: 
SFML 2 (git), cmake > 2.8, Boost > 1.38, C++ compiler

IF you have those, just issue "make go" and stuff should compile and launch.

